        "created_at": "2021-08-22T17:27:31.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p>Four of us are dining out tonight and bringing \u201cBecky\u201d wines to celebrate her life. I am trying to choose between 2002 and 1999 Bachelet Charmes-Chambertin, bith owned by me since release. I\u2019ve not had the 02 and actually stood it up a few weeks ago to try sometime soon. The 1999 I have had several times (but not since five years ago, when I found it relatively shut down but also only opened shortly before drinking in a restaurant) but stood up only a couple of days ago. Which would you choose and how much in advance would you double decant?</p>",
        "post_number": 1,
        "post_type": 1,
        "posts_count": 11,
        "updated_at": "2022-06-04T07:25:28.848Z",
