        "created_at": "2021-08-22T17:40:32.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p>For me, those are Denis\u2019 two best ever wines! With 1999 having the edge. Both are drinking very well now, but I\u2019d probably pick the 1999. I wouldn\u2019t double or single decant, the wine doesn\u2019t need it.</p>",
