        "avatar_template": "/user_avatar/www.wineberserkers.com/g_greenbaum/{size}/481_2.png",
        "created_at": "2021-08-24T15:18:02.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p>'99 Bachelet CC is one of the greatest wines I have ever tasted. It is, I believe, immortal. Please post a note. I opened '02 Mugnier Chambolle on Sunday and it was outstanding. I\u2019m not sure what it is about Mugnier, but his wines just reach another level of joy for me.</p>",
