        "created_at": "2021-08-24T16:15:50.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p>Had the 96 Bachelet Charmes a year ago, and it was remarkably good.  It was double decanted 3 hours before, and still needed a little air to get rolling.  Hard to go against William\u2019s advice, but with still experiencing some partially closed 99\u2019s currently, i would have suggested double decanting the 99 a couple of hours ahead.</p>",
